data.description: The award winning, AAA Four-Diamond Naples Bay Resort is located in downtown Naples on 5th Avenue South, and is the only hotel in Southwest Florida with its own fully operational yacht club and marina with direct access to the Gulf of Mexico. The resort's amenities include The Spa and a fitness center; full-service tennis center; four swimming pools; a lagoon-style, lazy river; and private cabanas. The resort's 97-slip marina incorporates a yacht club, waterfront pool, ship's store, fuel dock and rental boats. Adding to the experience is a 33,000-square-foot retail promenade, featuring high-end specialty boutiques. For more information, please call 239-530-5400 or visit NaplesBayResort.com.
